HHHHH.label: The Enlightened Leader
HHHHH.description: Curious, disciplined, outgoing, kind, and emotionally aware. A natural leader with high emotional intelligence.

HHHHL.label: The Visionary Diplomat
HHHHL.description: Inventive, reliable, socially skilled, cooperative, and emotionally stable. Great at guiding others and building bridges.

HHHLH.label: The Passionate Performer
HHHLH.description: Creative, organized, charismatic, assertive, and emotionally expressive. Thrives in dynamic, public environments.

HHHLL.label: The Independent Idealist
HHHLL.description: Imaginative and structured, yet introverted and blunt. Strives for truth over harmony.

HHLHH.label: The Charismatic Reactor
HHLHH.description: Thoughtful and unconventional, struggles with emotional turbulence but excels at inspiring others.

HHLHL.label: The Unpredictable Artist
HHLHL.description: Highly creative and principled, but emotionally steady and often distant. Expresses through abstract forms.

HHLLH.label: The Analytical Rebel
HHLLH.description: Innovative and introverted, resistant to rules but deeply sensitive inside.

HHLLL.label: The Detached Visionary
HHLLL.description: Independent, logical, and emotionally distant. Values thought over connection.

HLHHH.label: The Fiery Advocate
HLHHH.description: Empathetic yet impulsive. Low on structure but high on social drive and emotional intensity.

HLHHL.label: The Vibrant Connector
HLHHL.description: Warm, spontaneous, and full of life. Prefers chaos over routine but deeply values harmony.

HLHLH.label: The Empathetic Strategist
HLHLH.description: Creative and emotionally insightful, yet assertive and unafraid of conflict. Balances heart and head.

HLHLL.label: The Expressive Maverick
HLHLL.description: Energetic and persuasive, but emotionally stable and unapologetically individualistic.

HLLHH.label: The Sensitive Idealist
HLLHH.description: Kind-hearted and emotionally intense, yet often disorganized and introspective.

HLLHL.label: The Intuitive Wanderer
HLLHL.description: Unconventional and curious with a soft demeanor. Dislikes routine and avoids conflict.

HLLLH.label: The Lone Visionary
HLLLH.description: Quiet, original, sensitive, and slightly chaotic. Expresses through solitude and deep thought.

HLLLL.label: The Elusive Thinker
HLLLL.description: Detached from structure and low in sociability, yet highly imaginative and philosophical.

LHHHH.label: The Loyal Realist
LHHHH.description: Grounded, dependable, and sensitive. Seeks harmony and stability in a chaotic world.

LHHHL.label: The Social Strategist
LHHHL.description: Disciplined, sociable, and emotionally grounded. Excels in managing group dynamics.

LHHLH.label: The Compassionate Achiever
LHHLH.description: Structured, ambitious, and sensitive to others’ needs. Driven by purpose and empathy.

LHHLL.label: The Grounded Realist
LHHLL.description: Practical and persistent. Values results, avoids drama, and prefers predictability.

LHLHH.label: The Expressive Sentinel
LHLHH.description: Emotionally in tune and supportive, but avoids chaos and prefers routine.

LHLHL.label: The Warm Minimalist
LHLHL.description: Reserved and steady, but deeply caring. Keeps things simple and values deep connections.

LHLLH.label: The Pragmatic Thinker
LHLLH.description: Introverted but deeply rational. Balanced emotionality and a strong moral compass.

LHLLL.label: The Structured Observer
LHLLL.description: Detail-oriented and organized, with a tendency toward solitude.

LLHHH.label: The Tender Explorer
LLHHH.description: Emotionally rich and adventurous, but often lacks follow-through. Guided by heart and curiosity.

LLHHL.label: The Relational Drifter
LLHHL.description: Compassionate and engaging, but scattered. Thrives in the moment, avoids hard rules.

LLHLH.label: The Emotional Realist
LLHLH.description: Feels deeply and sees clearly. Honest and loyal, but struggles with emotional regulation.

LLHLL.label: The Gentle Disruptor
LLHLL.description: Quietly rebellious, kind, and skeptical of systems. Doesn’t like to be boxed in.

LLLHH.label: The Chaotic Thinker
LLLHH.description: Unstructured, sensitive, and highly perceptive. Often lost in thought or feeling.

LLLHL.label: The Quiet Helper
LLLHL.description: Introverted and steady, avoids confrontation. Gentle and observant, a calming presence.

LLLLH.label: The Internal Storm
LLLLH.description: Low in structure and sociability, but emotionally intense. Often misunderstood but deeply insightful.

LLLLL.label: The Detached Observer
LLLLL.description: Low across the board. Independent and rational, but emotionally distant and withdrawn.
